                            20.7044 10.2389C20.7044 11.4694 20.2156 12.6495 19.3455 13.5196C18.4754 14.3897 17.2953
                            14.8786 16.0648 14.8786C14.8342 14.8786 13.6541 14.3897 12.784 13.5196C11.9139 12.6495
